      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 4,
      "message": "This value isn't used by docker. Docker in current version didn't support the DOCKER_OPTS variables for OS base on the systemd. Current cmdline looks like -> ExecStart=/usr/bin/dockerd -H fd:// --containerd=/run/containerd/containerd.sock and didn't use DOCKER_OPTS.",
